{"service_name": "Security, Risk Management and Accreditation Service", "service_id": "7425470129371260", "company_name": "Actica Consulting", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Actica Consulting\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Security, Risk Management and Accreditation Service\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Actica Consulting provides expert security advice on all aspects of information assurance and cyber security relating to the Cloud, including the implications of the HMG Security Policy Framework (SPF), the Government Classification Scheme, ISO27001, the Data Protection Act and the Privacy and Electronic Communications Regulations.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Risk assessment consultancy, including IS1&amp;2, CRAMM, ISO27005, OCTAVE, IRAM\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Risk management and accreditation document set (RMADS) production\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Security requirements and security architecture production, including agile methods\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     PSN Code of Connection (CoCo) compliance assessment\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Business Impact Assessment, Privacy Impact Assessment (PIA) to ICO guidelines\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Protective Monitoring, Incident Management, Forensic Readiness advice\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Business Continuity Planning (BCP) and Disaster Recovery Plans (DRP) production\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Supplier security assurance and supporting compliance, audit and review activities\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     IT Health Check and penetration testing (CHECK, CREST, Tiger, PCI)\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     CESG Certified Professional (CCP) Cyber Security (formerly CLAS) consultant led\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Successful accreditation of your service\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Secure operation of your service\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Reduced operational risks\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ensure security is an enabler and not a constraint\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Enables a proportionate response to cyber security threats\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Effective management of Government policy changes\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Sectors: defence, education, fire, health, justice, local authority, police, transport\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3100 per person per hour\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92192/7425470129371260-pricing-document-2015-10-05-2046.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92192/7425470129371260-sfia-rate-card-2015-10-05-2046.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-it